- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about end-to-end automatic speech recognition (ASR) using modern architectures, which falls under the domain of natural language processing (NLP).
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with acoustic models for ASR.
- cs.LG (Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses both supervised and semi-supervised learning approaches for ASR.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques for ASR.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with developing an ASR system.
